## 9. Plan de Livraison (6 Sprints × 2 semaines)

```
Sprint 1 — Foundation
  ✓ Init Next.js + Spring Boot monorepo
  ✓ Auth (JWT, API Keys, RBAC)
  ✓ PostgreSQL schema + Flyway migrations
  ✓ Redis setup
  ✓ CI/CD pipeline (GitHub Actions)

Sprint 2 — Core Payment (Carte)
  ✓ Intégration Stripe (PaymentIntent)
  ✓ Endpoint POST /v1/payments
  ✓ Idempotency (Redis + PG)
  ✓ Webhook Stripe inbound (signature verification)

Sprint 3 — Méthodes de Paiement Étendues
  ✓ Apple Pay / Google Pay (Stripe Payment Request)
  ✓ SEPA Direct Debit
  ✓ SWIFT (instructions + statut manuel)
  ✓ Refund endpoint

Sprint 4 — Webhooks Outbound
  ✓ Kafka consumers (payment events)
  ✓ Dispatch webhook marchand (HMAC-SHA256)
  ✓ Retry scheduler (exponential backoff)
  ✓ Dashboard webhooks (liste + retry)

Sprint 5 — Analytics Temps Réel
  ✓ SSE bridge Kafka → Next.js
  ✓ Dashboard KPIs (volume, taux, latence)
  ✓ Graphes séries temporelles (Recharts)
  ✓ Table transactions avec filtres

Sprint 6 — Hardening & MMP Ready
  ✓ OpenTelemetry tracing distribué
  ✓ Rate limiting par marchand
  ✓ Pentest & audit PCI-DSS
  ✓ Documentation API (OpenAPI 3.1 + Swagger UI)
  ✓ Runbook opérationnel
```

